ActAvoiding Complicity in Mistreatment by Foreign Entities Act
SubjectAvoiding Complicity in Mistreatment by Foreign Entities ** Deputy Minister of Transport **
PrecisOrder authorizing the ISSUANCE of written directions to the Deputy Minister of Transport respecting the disclosure of, and request for information required bythe AVOIDING COMPLICITY IN MISTREATMENT BY FOREIGN ENTITIES ACT, in order to demonstrate that a whole-of-government ownership and responsibility for avoiding complicity in mistreatment, and broaden the application of measures to prevent mistreatment to government as a whole.
